# Bike-test captures: keep the text logs (logs/*.log) in the repo, but never the
# heavy binary artifacts (H.264 dumps, zipped bundles, the scrcpy download).

# The built APK is distributed via GitHub Releases (not committed — keeps the repo small).
*.apk

# Bike-test captures stay LOCAL. They are written before redaction runs, so they
# hold the wifi password, the OTA credentials and the vehicle serial in the clear.
logs/
